{"tid":2233010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"宣道小學教師遭釘牌 舊生親述課堂情況：佢係一個公平公正客觀嘅老師","createTime":"2020-10-06T22:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T02:08:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"70d8e6234f3a09016bd390e1d51d1073690fcc0a","tid":2233010,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T22:23:51.000Z","msg":"李同學稱，涉事教師對學生非常好，「我可以好肯定咁講，佢係一個公平公正嘅老師，而且係好客觀嘅，佢都係好客觀咁講佢睇法畀我哋聽嘅」。她上過課堂後，更加認識香港法律、反思何謂言論自由之餘，也更了解時下青少年對港獨的看法，「知道呢個香港發生緊咩事」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/JTPRRPWHJ5CBLDDKN5LNAOC5OI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FJTPRRPWHJ5CBLDDKN5LNAOC5OI%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmXpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=c998cf44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FJTPRRPWHJ5CBLDDKN5LNAOC5OI%2F&h=bf8623e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/JTPRRPWHJ5CBLDDKN5LNAOC5OI/</a>"},{"pid":"ad4cfad557337ad3a9bc7660f35c94f1f21697f8","tid":2233010,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T22:26:39.000Z","msg":"港共要殺雞儆猴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03aea4f577f7a03b95d5a448a122bad6cda9d4ca","tid":2233010,"uid":78039,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T22:33:26.000Z","msg":"港獨如佛地魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2a04f18749869bfbeddbc1f32aaf278fa8adb2","tid":2233010,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"03aea4f577f7a03b95d5a448a122bad6cda9d4ca","tid":2233010,"uid":78039,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T22:33:26.000Z","msg":"港獨如佛地魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T22:35:02.000Z","msg":"比喻唔好，因為佛地魔係大反派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c